MPI CORP (6223)  said unconsolidated sales
in May fell 31.82% to NT$242,223,000 from NT$355,249,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2012           5/2011
Sales            242,223          355,249    
YOY%             -31.82%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            933,802         1,741,580   
YOY%             -46.38% 
=================================================================
 